metadata.name: NFA TICKET #BLUE
metadata.description:
NFA Comics #1 can be burned for 1 of 3 NFA Tickets to progress to the next stage of the game.  
Each NFA Ticket has hidden value which will determine its mint power for the next stage of the game. 
The NFA Tickets value will be randomly assigned after the mint event concludes.  
PS : It's up to each Fool to decide how they will play this game of CHANCE.

NFA COLLECTION : https://opensea.io/collection/notorious-fool-academy  
NFA COMICS : https://opensea.io/collection/nfa-comics
